One comment:  I would protect the env, because install() and 
NewInteger() could each trigger a garbage collection.  That is, use

SEXP env;
PROTECT(env = NewEnv(R_GlobalEnv));
defineVar(install("OK"),NewInteger(0),env);
UNPROTECT(1);

Duncan Murdoch

